{
  "stem": "10588.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to tear up everything in order to examine for myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know what I discovered?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only the person who thinks with his own mind is free and who makes his own choices, who doesn't follow orders, who only accepts orders that he likes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, nowadays if somebody gives me an order, I know right away, this is not a person I want to associate, because the first sign of respect is when you want something-- I tell them, I honor requests.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't take orders, only from God, you know,",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The poem is called 'The Silent Voice,' and it was written May 11, 1980. 'Dedicated to all those whose voices have been silenced forever in the Holocaust from 1933 'til 1945.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When ages of civilization crumble to dust and death is raging supreme, when the devil is crowned by the power of deceit, then freedom is a faraway thing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When all that you have loved is taken from you and you are stripped to the bare bone, when all moral boundaries and laws are broken, then you are in hell with Satan alone.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When Jews are depicted as subhuman, as vermin, and brute force and evil prevail, when doctors and nurses turn children to corpses, then all logic and reason fail.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the whole world remains dead silent, with the exception of just a few, then they grant Satan license and opportunity to murder in the gas chambers a God-loving Jew.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When men and women are kept apart and new life is not conceived, when there is no sound of laughter or song, how can God by man be perceived?",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
